<Mod
    name="Electrum"
    description="Welcome to Electrum, a mod focused on the alchemy side of the game. This mod aims to make the alchemy parts of the game both less tedious, and more rewarding.

for bug reports, proper documentation, and feature suggestions, go to the github page: https://github.com/CrazyAmphibian/Electrum

Overview:
- integration with other mods
- 22 spells (2 more with other mods)
- 15 materials
- 5 new items
- 1 new perk


Spells:
	This mod adds spells that summon potions and new materials.
	Additionally, there's added utility spells to help you along your alchemy journey
	Some spells are a bit gimmicky, but can prove to be quite useful if used correctly.


Materials:
	This mod adds a few precursors to more impactful materials.
	Why not relax with a nice flask of hot chocolate?
	play your cards right, and you might even find a way to become immune to polymorphing... for a short time.
	There's also additional reactions to help you get more materials in the game, such as gunpowder and honey.


Items:
	An unbreakable flask helps ease worries with dangerous materials.
	A new storage flask is tailored for aggressive play.
	Some special wands will prove especially useful.


Perk:
	A new perk has been added that gives you a private alchemy lab, though it must be earned first.



